high_descs: walk straight then turn right to the left side of the sink
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink
Turn right  walk forward then face the counter on your left
Slice the cabbage on the counter
Turn left head to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn right head to the counter with cabbage
Pick up a slice of cabbage
Turn left head to the sink
Put in the cabbage in the sink and rinse it
Turn right then walk towards the end of the counter
Put the slice cabbage in the trash bin  under the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the slice cabbage in the trash bin  under the counter

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the bin.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the bin.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce in the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the bin.
Put the slice of lettuce in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of lettuce in the bin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Turn right and walk forward and turn left to face the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Place the knife in the right side of the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce slice in the sink and remove it.
Turn right and walk forward and turn left to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the lettuce slice in the trash can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: To wash a lettuce slice and place it in the trash.
